00","end":"1627128300","first":"G","idtitle":"GRANDEURNATUREDANSLEPARCNATURELHAUTESFAGNESEIFEL","title":"Grandeur Nature dans le Parc naturel Hautes Fagnes-Eifel","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2Face73947-cdc0-46ab-81b9-8e67717bb873-fre,imi:1ca3b5a6f6e6c90c3e2b28b2330eff0d066be5db","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/a8f__b88__a8fb8817-f558-413c-84c6-7c3daa1ec171__B105934544.jpg","description":"Tout au long des cinq \u00e9missions TV de 26 minutes, Adrien Joveneau nous propose de d\u00e9couvrir diff\u00e9rents Parcs naturels de Wallonie en compagnie de personnes inspirantes. Chaque rencontre nous donne l'occasion d'appr\u00e9cier la nature tout en adoptant les bons gestes pour la pr\u00e9server. \n Retrouvez \u00e9galement Grandeur Nature via les diff\u00e9rentes plateformes digitales de la RTBF o\u00f9 seront partag\u00e9s des contenus in\u00e9dits ainsi que sur Vivacit\u00e9 d\u00e8s la rentr\u00e9e de septembre.","category":"Documentaire, Natuur"},"3039489":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:launehd","start":"1627128300","end":"1627130100","first":"U","idtitle":"UNMONDEAPART","title":"Un monde \u00e0 part","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2F73a5c870-1734-46ec-b967-b10aac141041-fre,imi:ec947df875d1e688b268b5f45906c6653b76a4eb","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/9de__fd5__9defd5bc-94cf-4cd7-8de8-39dcd9c7f2fc__W203710120.jpg","description":"Fran\u00e7ois Mazure trekt in deze aflevering op met de rangers in het Virungapark, een nationaal park in het oosten van de Democratische Republiek Congo, dat bekend is om zijn berggorilla's.","category":"Nieuws, Actualiteitenprogramma's"},"3039571":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:launehd","start":"1627130100","end":"1627131600","first":"T","idtitle":"TOOCUTE","title":"Too Cute!","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2F6c5da480-46a4-42b8-be60-d7294757f379-fre,imi:77058ae2be0311a01baf865c2f7aaa2098dcbfc9","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/9e8__f2b__9e8f2b7d-b7b9-44f1-a37c-62e885c21bec__B49725648.jpg","description":"Volg de ontwikkeling van drie nestjes jonge dieren in verschillende fasen. Heel voorzichtig, stap voor stap, verkennen de kittens de wereld om zich heen.","category":"Documentaire, Natuur"},"3039642":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:launehd","start":"1627131600","end":"1627141200","first":"C","idtitle":"CYCLISME","title":"Cyclisme","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2F3c0c217f-f610-4fd4-890e-04ac5bb95baf-fre,imi:46f50040494fbf426a40b42586a1dfddabadb036","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/384__da0__384da0be-7660-453a-9e73-06b7483e2d2e__B106321634.jpg","description":"Cinqui\u00e8me et derni\u00e8re \u00e9tape de ce Tour de Wallonie entre Dinant et Quaregnon. Apr\u00e8s un parcours l\u00e9g\u00e8rement vallon\u00e9 de 183 kilom\u00e8tres, on connaitra enfin le vainqueur de cette 42\u00e8me \u00e9dition du Tour de Wallonie. Commentaires de Samu\u00ebl Grulois et G\u00e9rard Bulens.","category":"Sport, Wielrennen"},"3040627":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:launehd","start":"1627141200","end":"1627141500","first":"N","idtitle":"NOSCHERSVOISINS","title":"Nos chers voisins","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2F39116ef5-61d6-4577-bbbb-131efc435820-fre,imi:7a3e8532b46c429bbd62de2feedcd697015b1e73","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/04c__c6c__04cc6c8d-439e-4b1a-ab42-d83eb0dfc8e4__B142863630.jpg","description":"Franse komische serie","category":"Sitcoms"},"3040900":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:launehd","start":"1627141500","end":"1627143300","first":"H","idtitle":"HANHOMMESANIMAUXNATURE","title":"H.A.N. , Hommes Animaux Nature","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2Fa9b3daf5-0429-438a-a517-3a094821808a-fre,imi:e86573eccbb262368a48d55e8314218f647384bb","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/a40__857__a40857e1-c9bc-4537-9e1e-3f0ff04a6293__B128513530.jpg","description":"Le domaine de Han accueille une nouvelle locataire, une jeune femelle lynx, qui vient rejoindre le couple d\u00e9j\u00e0 pr\u00e9sent. Plusieurs esp\u00e8ces d'oiseaux vivent \u00e9galement \u00e0 Han : des chouettes lapones \u00e0 l'ou\u00efe impressionnante, des cigognes blanches qui viennent de pondre et des cigognes noires, plus discr\u00e8tes. L'une d'elles est bless\u00e9e au bec et requiert l'intervention de Goulven. C'est aussi la fin de l'hibernation des marmottes et de la quarantaine de deux aurochs attaqu\u00e9s par... des poux.","category":"Documentaire, Natuur"},"3041007":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:launehd","start":"1627143300","end":"1627145400","first":"S","idtitle":"STOEMPPEKETETDESRAWETTES","title":"Stoemp, p\u00e8k\u00e8t... et des rawettes !","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2Ff85549cd-11d8-45fd-9833-e3ed834d9030-fre,imi:93da92406ef90ef18ad32fac032d2531973779d5","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/d6a__3b6__d6a3b6fc-b2fb-4579-adf8-75c5f0aafcea__B155268530.jpg","description":"Met vandaag: journaliste en presentatrice Oph\u00e9lie Fontana.","category":"Nieuws, Actualiteitenprogramma's"},"3041093":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:launehd","start":"1627145400","end":"1627147260","first":"D","idtitle":"DESNOUNOUSPOURANIMAUX","title":"Des nounous pour animaux","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2F3fb94de1-3968-4a13-abd5-3527d191c689-fre,imi:3e1584317cd42ae9f384140cb8751a8f4ce16fe8","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/3ff__b79__3ffb79ef-7bc6-492a-8ad3-f3939b6eae99__B160044812.jpg","description":"Afrique du Sud. Alphie, un singe vervet de 10 semaines, s'appr\u00eate \u00e0 prendre un bain et \u00e0 faire sa premi\u00e8re excursion dans la nature avec sa nounou, Silke. En Espagne, sur l'\u00eele de Teneriffe, Juan, un jeune dauphin n\u00e9 en captivit\u00e9 \u00e0 l'Europark, va se produire pour la premi\u00e8re fois en public avec sa m\u00e8re et sa grand-m\u00e8re. Il s'entra\u00eene depuis des mois avec son dresseur, Miguel. En Allemagne, dans une station de protection pour animaux sauvages, Mareen s'occupe de toutes sortes d'orphelins : renardeaux, marcassins...","category":"Documentaire, Natuur"},"3041450":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:launehd","start":"1627147260","end":"1627147500","first":"M","idtitle":"METEOLAUNE","title":"M\u00e9t\u00e9o La Une","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2F6c23aace-e6f0-4886-8655-e9e6216e8b3a-fre,imi:ba65ffa629c10f7bc1dfa59a862f60a457218034","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/450__42e__45042e00-1e40-47b2-a4e3-34d9d2d8e865__B179167867.jpg","description":"Tout au long de la journ\u00e9e, retrouvez les pr\u00e9visions m\u00e9t\u00e9orologiques nationales et les bons conseils pour ne pas \u00eatre surpris par le temps.","category":"Nieuws, Weer"},"3041457":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:launehd","start":"1627147500","end":"1627147800","first":"M","idtitle":"METEODESVACANCES","title":"M\u00e9t\u00e9o des vacances","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~~2Fd005455c-7eef-4f94-94d4-17070bec6b80-fre,imi:4371316dfed480b98f4f7a75d049d52a566c9e0d","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/staticqbr-be-prod.tnprod.cdn.dmdsdp.com\/image-service\/ImagesEPG\/EventImages\/4fd__791__4fd79126-c92c-4544-856c-a53e2f5c6868__W51082771.jpg","description":"Retrouvez les pr\u00e9visions m\u00e9t\u00e9orologiques de la c\u00f4te belge et des c\u00f4tes europ\u00e9ennes.","category":"Nieuws, Weer"},"3041485":{"channel":"lgi-be-prod-master:launehd","start":"1627147800","end":"1627149900","first":"J","idtitle":"JT19H30","title":"JT 19h30","program_id":"crid:~~2F~~2Ftelenet.be~